VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(?:password|secret|api_key|apikey|token|private_key)\s*=\s*"[A-Za-z0-9@#$%^&*!_\-]{8,}"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:var\.|data\.|local\.|sensitive
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects hardcoded credentials or secrets directly assigned as Terraform resource attribute values.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Hardcoded Secret or Password in Terraform Variables.
